OL,5, A chess commentator has been sacked by 
OL,6, the International Chess Federation for 
OL,7, making sexist comments.                
OL,9,FIlya Smirin was broadcasting live      
OL,10,Fduring the ninth round of the Women's  
OL,11,FGrand Prix on Tuesday.                 
OL,13,FThe Israeli grandmaster admitted on air
OL,14,Fhe had said chess is "maybe not for    
OL,15,Fwomen" - and also seemingly praised a  
OL,16,Fwoman for playing like a man.          
OL,18,FThe federation apologised and called Mr
OL,19,FSmirin's comments offensive and        
OL,20,Fembarrassing.                          
